title: Prince - Alphabet St. (U.S. Promo) PRO-CD-3079 - PRNArchive - PR
description:
This is the U.S. Promo CD single of Price's "Alphabet St."


It contains the only release on CD, of the rare-to-find Single Edit of the song.


Note that although four tracks are listed, tracks #2 and #3 appear to be exactly the same!
